T02D3695:328a-1: a'arya t'a r'a de b'i sto tra /
T02D3695:328a-3: 'phags ma lha mo sgrol ma la bstod pa /
T02D3695:328a-4: rje btsun 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3695:328a-5: lha mo sgrol ma lha yi lha //
T02D3695:328a-6: 'jig rten gsum na mchog gyur pa //
T02D3695:328a-7: thugs rje chen po'i dbang gyur pas //
T02D3695:328a-8: khams gsum 'gro ba sgrol la mkhas //
T02D3695:328a-9: tshor ba btang snyoms ngo bo nyid ;
T02D3695:328a-10: / mi mthun tshor ba bde sdug ldan /
T02D3695:328a-11: phrag dog 'joms pa'i phrin las can //
T02D3695:328a-12: mkha' ltar dangs pa bla na med //
T02D3695:328a-13: gzung ba dang ni 'dzin pa yi //
T02D3695:328a-14: rnam rtog spangs pa'i bde ba can //

T02D3695:328a-27: shin tu mi bzad thabs ldan pa'i //

T02D3695:328a-29: seng ge glang po stag dang sprul //
T02D3695:328a-30: chom rkun me chu sha za yi //
